The paper discusses the development of lifelong learning systems and efficient algorithms for learning new internal representations. This topic is closely related to several sub-categories of computer science, including machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), and neural networks (cs.NE). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
